OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA day of sunny spells and
OL,6,Fblustery showers, with the most
OL,7,Ffrequent showers towards the north of
OL,8,Fthe region. Isolated chance of hail
OL,9,Fand the odd rumble of thunder.
OL,10,FTemperatures a little below average.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers becoming less
OL,13,Ffrequent into the evening, before
OL,14,Fskies cloud over from the west later
OL,15,Fin the night, with showery outbreaks
OL,16,Fof rain reaching the area towards dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
